Pair of windows with full installation kit

Product Name: Victron Energy Orion-Tr 12/12 18A Isolated Battery Charger
Product Description:
Victron Energy Orion-Tr 12/12 18A Isolated Battery Charger

Adaptive 3-stage charger for dual battery systems

The Orion-Tr smart battery charger is ideal for use in vehicles with two or more batteries. The Orion is compatible with the smart alternators used in modern vehicles, and can also detect when your engine and alternator are in operation, and adapt charging to suit.

Programmable with wireless control

The Orion-Tr Smart comes equipped with Bluetooth, allowing you to configure, monitor and control your Victron charger with your smartphone. It can be optimised for both lead acid and lithium batteries. The charger uses a 3-stage system with bulk, absorption and float, optimising your charging rate while protecting you battery health.

With short circuit protection

The Orion features short circuit protection, as well as high temperature protection and an IP43 rating.

Victron Energy Orion-Tr 12/12 18A features:

  • Configurable charge algorithm
  • 3-stage charging with bulk, float and absorption stages
  • Suitable for vehicles with smart alternators
  • Includes two-pole on-off relay contact
  • Can be installed in parallel to increase output
  • High temperature protection
  • IP43 rated
  • Input fuse included

Product Name: Adventurer 12v Vehicle Battery To Leisure Battery Charger with Engine Trickle Charge
Product Description:
Adventurer 12 V battery DC to DC charger (leisure battery to vehicle battery) with built-in trickle charge

No more flat engine battery when you’re ready to getaway!

Keeps your vehicle starter battery ready to go even after a long lay up!

The Adventurer battery to battery charger from Jacksons is the ideal companion for your campervan or motor home vehicle battery and leisure battery, utilising the leisure battery to keep your engine battery in a boosted state.  

Standard and Unique feature!

The standard feature is that while in transit your motorhome chargers up your leisure battery. However its unique feature is that the vehicle battery is topped up by the leisure battery when there is surplus power available, thus ensuring you don’t end up with a flat vehicle battery when your campervan or motor home has been parked up for a while.

Using its "smart sensing system"

The Adventurer B2B charger will monitor your leisure battery voltage state. If its fully charged - and the vehicle starter battery is less than 12.6v - it will trickle charge the motorhome or campervan battery with any spare power back to 12.6v whilst not draining you leisure battery below 13.06v.  It’s the perfect system which is especially enhanced by motor homes and campervans with solar panels.

Plug-and-play installation

Multistage charging profiles automatically control battery charging, with both bulk and float-maintained battery charging. The charging profile in use is indicated via a visual LED indicator on the charger unit, so you can always see what the charger unit is doing. The unit is designed for quick and simple plug and play vehicle installation, using a simple design with broad compatibility.

Download the APP

Requires the purchase of the Bluetooth Connector, its easy to set up, download the app and you’re away.  This handy little bit of kit allows you to monitor, control and configure your Adventurer DC to DC charger and trickle charger.  This option is required when Lithium batteries are being used.

Adventurer 12V 30A DC-DC Charger Features:

  • Compatible with all engine classes/alternator types (smart and constant)
  • Suitable for stop-start technology and regenerative braking
  • Can charge batteries DC-DC
  • 2A Trickle charge to starter battery (when surplus power available)
  • Suitable for most automotive batteries of lead acid chemistry, AGM, GEL, sealed – flooded
  • Total charging capacity up to a maximum of 300 Amp Hours battery capacity
  • Can be configured for lithium batteries with the optional Bluetooth module and free app
  • Optional Bluetooth module available for battery voltage monitoring and advance configurations
  • Ideal for installation in campervans, motorhomes and more
  • Lithium Batteries:  This device is not compatible with Lithium batteries unless connected to the optional APP via the Bluetooth module.

Product Name: CAN Combi Sink and Hob Single Burner Campervan Conversion Kit 1 - FL1323 FL1324
Product Description:
CAN Combi Sink and Hob Single Burner Campervan Conversion Kit 1

Containing all the essentials to connect your FL1323 or FL1324 sink and hob

Our campervan conversion kits provide all the fittings required to set up your sink and hob cooker. The CAN single hob combi is a perfect fit for smaller campervans, giving you all the essentials in a small, sleek package. 

The easy way to get running water and gas cooking in your camper

Our kit includes two jerry cans to carry your fresh and waste water, a tap and 12v pump (and the pipe and fittings to connect them), and a gas regulator with gas hose and fittings. You can also customise the kit to suit your campervan conversion - we have both cold and hot tap options, a gaz regulator option for more lightweight or temporary installations, and a bulkhead option for more permanent installations.

Luxury stainless steel sink and hob

The CAN single burner combi comes complete with a tempered glass lid with a smoked finish, allowing you to preserve worktop space when it's not in use. The lid hinges are recessed, keeping your worktop as flush as possible. The pan support grid uses rubber washers to reduce wobble, too. The piezo ignition requires no power, ensuring you can use your cooker even in remote off-grid locations.

CAN Combi Sink features:

  • Smoked, tempered heat resistant glass lid
  • Recessed 'disappearing' hinges for flush worktop
  • Piezo ignition for power-free startup
  • Robust 304L stainless steel construction
  • Powerful 1900w gas burner
  • 27mm tap hole pre-drilled for easy set-up

The CAN combi kit 1 contains:

•    CAN sink and hob combi unit
•    Cold Tap or Hot & Cold Mixer Tap
•    Whale Submersible Pump
•    2 x 9.5L Jerry Cans
•    2mtr x 10mm Cold Pipe
•    2mtr x 20mm Waste Pipe
•    2mtr x 10mm Hot Pipe (Only available when mixer tap selected)
•    1 x 75mm Floor Vent
•    Pack of x 5 P Clips
•    4 x Jubilee Clips

Camping Gaz option includes:

•    1x Camping Gaz Regulator
•    1x 8mm Compression Nozzle
•    1mtr LPG Gas Hose

Bulkhead option includes:

•    1 x 8mm Bulkhead Regulator
•    1 x 45cm Pigtail
•    1 x 8mm 90° Compression Elbow
•    1 x Gaz Adapter
•    2mtr x 8mm Copper Pipe
•    1x 8mm Straight Compression Coupling

Product Name: Whale Aquasource Clear 15mm Water System Filter - WF1530
Product Description:
Whale Aquasource Clear 15mm Water System Filter - WF1530

Remove unpleasant tastes from your water system

Whale's Aquasource water system uses silver-impregnated activated carbon to filter impurities from your water system. This leaves your campervan, caravan motorhome or boat's water tasting fresh and clean. The filter uses a maintenance-free design which lasts for once full season - or 4500 litres of water. The filter connects directly to 15mm quick-fit water connectors for easy installation - they're typically fitted under the sink, and can be mounted both vertically and horizontally.

How to drain the Whale Aquasource Water Filter for winterisation

  • Open all taps in the caravan
  • Open the drain valve
  • Tilt caravan so drain plug is lowest
  • Let the water run out of drain valve

Product Name: Maxview Roam 3G 4G WiFi Router for Caravan & Motorhome
Product Description:
Maxview Roam 3G/4G WiFi Router With 5G Ready Antenna for Caravan & Motorhome

High-speed signal for your travels

The Maxview Roam lets you utilise 3G and 4G signals to create a WiFi network in your home away from home. The antenna is omni-directional, ensuring no adjustments are necessary, and the router comes complete with an aluminium housing and anti-vibration mounting. The router also features two ethernet ports for direct connections to laptops and other devices.

How it works

The Roam uses a sleek roof-mount antenna, allowing it to pick up signals even where your smartphone can't. The antenna uses a standard mobile SIM card. This antenna connects to the router, which creates a WiFi network from the mobile data connection. A future-proof 5G ready antenna is included. If you are at a campsite with WiFi available, the Roam can also be used as a WiFi booster, using the powerful antenna to pick up the existing campsite WiFi connection and using the router to boost the signal to your devices.

With app support

The Maxview Roam has a smartphone app for iOS and Android, allowing you to easily configure and monitor your connection. This makes it easy to connect your 12v router to WiFi connections for signal boosting and more. The Maxview Roam router kit is suitable for campervan, caravan, motorhome and narrowboat.

Maxview Roam 3G/4G WiFi Router features:

  • Lightweight and streamlined antenna (5G ready)
  • Small but powerful router
  • Aluminium router casing with anti-vibration mounting
  • Two ethernet ports for stable wired laptop connection
  • Compatible with current 3G and 4G technology (when used a suitable SIM card)
  • Runs on 12v
  • Suitable for roaming & European travel (when used with suitable SIM card)

Maxview Roam contents:

  • Omnidirectional roof-mount antenna
  • 0.8m antenna cable with SMA connectors
  • WiFi router dome (Choice of white or dark grey)
  • 12v cigarette power supply
  • Router mounting kit
  • 1.5m ethernet cable
  • Instructions

Product Description:
Reimo Vertic Tailgate Tent Awning for VW Caddy or similar Mini Campervans

Let your van grow as your pitch

This handy tailgate tent lets you make the most of your mini camper. It's designed to fit the VW Caddy, but a universal design means it's also suitable for other similarly sized vehicles, including the Renault Kangoo (2008-) Mercedes Citan (2010-2012), Citroen Berlingo/Peugeot Partner Tepee (2008-) and the Fiat Doblo II (2010-).

Easy mounting

It uses robust ripstop polyester, with a UV resistant coating to preserve an even shade and a fire-retardant finish.

  • Lightweight package
  • Ripstop polyester fabric
  • Sealed seams
  • UV and fire resistant

Product Name: Winbond 60HV Primerless Adhesive Kit for Windows
Product Description:
Winbond 60HV Primerless Adhesive Starter Kit

Easy window installation without the need for primer

This specialised adhesive is designed for fixing windows directly to windows. It's ideal for installing windows to your campervan, extra glass in your panel van, or when repairing window damage. This starter kit comes with 310ml of adhesive, two adhesive cleaning wipes, and a pair of gloves for smear-free installation.

Primer-free & with UV resistance

Typical window adhesives, such as Winbond Ultra Cure, require a black primer to activate the adhesive - and also to act as a blackout on the edges. Winbond's 60HV formula achieves a high adhesion without the need for primer, and uses a silyl-terminated polymer with excellent UV stability - which, in layman's terms, means it doesn't need a blackout primer.

Usage tips

We recommend that you store the adhesive inside before use - application is easier when the adhesive is at room temperature. With 60HV adhesive, we advise you wait for a minimum of an hour before using your vehicle.

Winbond 60HV bonded window installation kit contents:

  • 1x Winbond 60HV primeless adhesive
  • 1x Surface cleaning wipe for adhesives & tapes
  • 1x Glass wipe for surface preparation
  • 1x Pair of gloves

Product Name: Wolfrace VW T5 T6 Explorer Sahara Matt Black Alloy Wheels
Product Description:
Wolfrace VW T5 T6 Explorer Sahara Matt Black Alloy Wheels - 8.5x18

The perfect upgrade for your VW T5 or T6

Elevate the appeal of your van with a set of Wolfrace Explorer alloys. Designed in the UK, these sleek alloy wheels are compatible with the VW T6, and come with an optional set of BF Goodrich all terrain tyres. Our wheels are sold as a set of four as standard.

With included fitting kit

All of our Wolfrace alloys come complete with an alloy wheel fitting kit, and if you select tyres these will be fitted, balanced and valved. Wolfrace's explorer alloys are designed for adventure, with a lightweight and sturdy construction. BF Goodrich tyres are a popular choice among campervan users, allowing your vehicle to maximise its grip on and off road.

Available in 18" or 20"

These wheels come in two sizes. The 18" wheels provide a more standard fitting, with tyre thickness close to stock. 20" wheels use a thinner tyre, providing a larger wheel with a low profile tyre. BF Goodrich all-terrain tyres use a thicker sidewall and thick grooves for high performance on and off-road, and this means they aren't available with the 20" rims - if you'd like to discuss alternative tyre choices for this size, please contact us.

Compatibility

  • VW T5 Transporter & Caravelle 2003-2009
  • VW T5.1 Transporter & Caravelle 2010-15
  • VW T6 Transporter & Caravelle 2015-19
  • VW T6.1 Transporter & Caravelle 2019 Onwards

Lightweight, sporty 17" alloy wheel rims

Improve the performance and aesthetics of your camper with a set of elegant Wolfrace Bayern alloy wheels. These come as a set of four, with an included wheel fitting kit. These sporty rims are lightweight, meaning they are likely to improve your vehicle's handling and fuel economy.

Tough design

Product Description:
CAN FL1765 FL1766 Combi Hob and Sink Conversion Kit 1

Kit for an easy and high-quality campervan conversion

We've created this conversion kit to give you everything you need to get your CAN sink and hob combi cooker up and running. CAN are a veteran manufacturer in the campervan cookware field, producing reliable, lightweight and robust designs that have garnered the trust of those in the industry.

Dual burner hob with integrated sink and tap hole

The CAN FL176x series combi sink and hob is designed for the leisure industry, with features ideal for caravan, campervan, motorhome and boat use. It uses two compact yet powerful gas burners, which are concealed by a tempered glass lid with recessed soft-close hinges. The pan supports are mounted on anti-vibration grommets, and the sink features a pre-drilled tap hole for easy installation.

With full kit of complementary conversion parts

We've included jerry cans, pipework and a pump to give you a compact and effective water system - as well as clips for a clean installation. You can choose between a cold water tap or a hot and cold mixer tap, too. As for the gas hobs, you can choose between either a gaz system for more temporary installations, or a bulkhead regulator system for more permanent ones. These are supplied with copper gas pipe or flexible gas hose, the appropriate regulator, as well as gas fixings.

CAN FL1765 FL1766 Conversion Kit 1 Contents:

  • CAN FL1765 or FL1766 combi hob (left or right - e.g. right has sink on right hand side)
  • Reich Samba micro switch Cold Tap or Hot & Cold Tap

  • 2 x 9.5L Jerry Cans

Camping gaz option includes:

Product Name: CBE CB522-LT Lithium 12V Battery Mains 230V Charger - Works with PC100 PC110 PC180 PC200 PC210
Product Description:
CBE CB522-LT Electronic Lithium Battery Charger

Dedicated lithium battery charger with up to 320w output

CBE has designed this charger to maximise efficiency while charging lithium battery systems. The CB522-LT manipulates both the voltage and current supplied to the battery in an intricate charging profile, which maximises the energy transfer. This charger makes the most of the fast charging capabilities of lithium batteries.

Four-phase charging system

CBE's research into lithium battery chemistry has allowed them to refine their charging profile, which can be simplified into four main phases. It begins with the bulk phase, where high current is used until end-of charge voltage is reached. The absorption phase follows to complete the charge at a lower current without damaging the battery. The battery is then maintained with the float phase, which returns to bulk if loads on the battery cause the voltage to drop below 12.7v. The final refresh phase provides high-voltage charging for a short period to maintain the battery.

Sargent Campervan Modular Power System with Touchscreen Display
Product Description:
Sargent Modular Power System with Touchscreen Display

Motorhome Battery, Heating, Lighting, Water Monitor with 4" or 7" Display

The Modular Power System with 4"/7" Display is a versatile, compact solution designed for flexible installation, ideal for motorhomes, campervans, and caravans. This system consists of two key components: the MC100 power hub and the MC200 mains protection unit, both working together to manage 12V and 230V power requirements. The MC100 acts as the central hub, providing power, switching, and monitoring for essential 12V accessories like heating, lighting, and water systems. Meanwhile, the MC200 ensures safety with RCD and MCB protection for 230V mains circuits, making it a reliable system for handling both DC and AC power needs. 

This modular power system is available with two different screen sizes; a 4" touchscreen display, and a 7" touchscreen display. The EC940 4" touchscreen display, allows for control over lighting, power, water levels, and environmental sensors. The display simplifies monitoring and management, giving you a clear view of system status in real time. Plus, the system is easily expandable through CAN Bus integration, allowing connection with additional accessories like lithium batteries, solar regulators, ultrasonic water sensors, and battery chargers. The larger 7" display screen allows for an intuitive monitoring system with an easy to read display. The 7" display allows for control and monitoring of lighting, power usage, water levels, and environmental sensors, enhancing usability and convenience.

This touchscreen display power system is ideal for monitoring and controlling power, lighting, water and environmental sensors in your motorhome. Also suitable for caravan, campervan, motorhome and van conversions. Expandable through integrating CAN Bus accessories including solar regulators, ultrasonic water sensors and lithium batteries. Ultimate power control for your motorhome or caravan!

Key Features:

  • MC100 Hub: Provides power, switching, and monitoring for 12V systems like heating, lighting, and water.
  • MC200 Mains Protection: Includes RCD and MCB protection for 230V mains circuits, ensuring safety.
  • EC940 Touchscreen Display: 4" intuitive touchscreen for easy control and monitoring of power, lighting, water, and more.
  • EC970 Touchscreen Display: Larger 7" touchscreen display for easy control and battery, power, lighting, water monitoring.
  • Expandable via CAN Bus: Easily connect intelligent accessories such as lithium batteries, solar regulators, and ultrasonic water sensors for a customized power solution.
  • Flexible Installation: Compact design allows for mounting as a single unit or separately in tight spaces.
  • Expandable Connectivity: Easily expand your system with intelligent CAN Bus accessories, including lithium batteries, solar regulators, ultrasonic water sensors, and battery chargers, allowing for customized power solutions.
  • Multiple Input Options: The MC100 hub features two 20A battery inputs and a 25A charger input, enabling efficient power management for leisure activities.
  • Comprehensive Monitoring: Track fresh and waste water levels with up to four fresh water inputs and one waste water input, ensuring effective management of onboard resources.

Product Name: Adventurer Fold-Down Steps for Campervans and Motorhomes With LED light
Product Description:
Steps for Campervans and Motorhomes

Fold-down steps for easy access in all conditions

Take a step into comfort with a fold-away step for your camper. Our campervan and motorhome steps are made from aluminium alloy, ensuring they are both strong and lightweight. What's more, the steps include integrated rubber grip-strips, providing slip resistance even in the wet.

Available with an electric motor for double step variant

For added convenience our single or double step is available in a manual or electric option. Alternatively the manual steps require no power connection to extend or retract the step, which means they can be used even when your leisure battery power is low. They are also designed to withstand a maximum static load of 200kg for added peace of mind. They are available as either a single step or dual step design.

Incorporated LED Strip

For added safety and peace of mind, both variants have LED strips on the edge of the tread, preventing trips and falls and offering a welcoming light to the campervan, caravan or motorhome. A switchable 12v power connection is required to operate the LED lights. 

Campervan and motorhome step features:

  • Aluminium alloy design
  • Strong and lightweight construction
  • Integrated rubber grip-strips
  • Available as a manual operation single/ double step or electric Double Step
  • Electric Double Step
  • Integrated LED strip in edge of each footplate
  • To operate the LED strip lights, a 12v switchable power connection is required

Shower and Bathroom Kit - C403 Toilet, Shower, Sink and Tray Kit for Campervan Conversions
Product Description:
Shower and Bathroom Kit - Toilet, Shower, Sink and Tray Kit for Campervan Conversions

Fully compatible bathroom kit for integrated water tanks

We've created this bathroom kit to take out the difficulty in choosing complementary bathroom components. All the products in this kit fit together - and we can vouch for their quality. We've also made sure they're at a great value price once bundled in this kit.

What's included?

In this kit you will receive ten of our most popular bathroom products:

  • Thetford C403 Cassette Toilet
  • Contessa tip-up sink
  • Shower tray compatible with the C403
  • Shower with installation bar
  • Mixer tap for basin
  • Mixer tap for shower
  • Waste outlet drain for shower tray
  • Waste outlet drain for basin

Ideal kit for bathrooms & water systems in campervan conversions and motorhomes

This bathroom kit includes the C403 toilet, which we offer in either left or right. Both come with the same feature set, including electric flush, LED level display and a large 19 litre wheeled waste tank. The Contessa tip-up basin sink is both lightweight and compact, designed around the needs of the camper bathroom. The shower tray too is designed to provide a bespoke fit around your Thetford C403 toilet, giving a flush, water-tight finish. 

We've included two mixer taps - one which fits with the Contessa sink, and another for the shower. The shower includes a rail for easy adjustments - just as you would have at home, but in a compact form. The waste outlets are the correct size for the shower tray and sink, allowing you to route waste water into your waste tank elegantly.

How much space do I need to fit a bathroom?

With this kit, your toilet fits flush against the shower tray. This means your bathroom can be as small as the size of the shower tray plus the size of the toilet. For smaller spaces, see our C250 bathroom kit.

  • Shower tray overall Size: L1050 x W670mm.
  • Shower well size: L780 x W545mm
  • C403 Dimensions: H512 x W670 x D400mm

Our Dometic 9722 universal conversion kit contains all you need to get your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat kitchen fully equipped. At the heart of this kit is the Dometic 9722 - a stainless steel sink and hob, beloved by commercial campervan converters for its build quality and performance.

Fully compatible parts

We've chosen a selection of parts and fittings to get you on the road as quickly as possibly. All of the components in this kit are quality parts which we've been selling to converters for many years - and are the right size to work with each other. This includes a Whale water pump, a waste and fresh water tank and pipes, a gas vent, p-clips, jubilee clips, gas pipe and fittings, and electrical cable and connectors.

Product Description:
Reimo Update Tailgate Tent for Mercedes Vito V-Class Micro Camper Vans

Awning for Mercedes Vito Campervans

This easy-to-use Reimo awning tent features a a window, roll-up door, as well as access into your vehicle. It's tailor made to provide a bespoke fit to the Mercedes Vito V-Class vans from 2015 onwards.

Lightweight design

Ideal for short trips away, this Reimo tailgate tent is quick to pitch and lightweight to carry. Tailgate tents use your vehicle's boot to provide rooftop rigidity, ensuring you get a tall and supported awning every time you pitch. This also means that the awning doesn't require any poles whatsoever - this is what allows it to weigh only 4.4kg, and makes it really easy to set up.

Robust fabric

The Reimo tailgate awning for the Mercedes Vito uses 100% ripstop polyester, which is coated in PU to offer water resistance. This gives the tent an excellent hydrostatic head of 3000mm, allowing it to withstand the British weather. The seams are sealed to prevent water seepage, and a UV and fire resistant coating has also been added to prevent damage in the heat.

Reimo Tailgate Tent for Mercedes Vito Features:

  • Lightweight 4.4kg design
  • Rapid pitching time
  • PVC window
  • 100% ripstop polyester
  • Waterproof PU coating
  • UV and fire resistant coating
  • 3000mm hydrostatic head

Product Name: Adventurer Campervan & Motorhome Battery Trickle Charger
Product Description:
Adventurer Campervan and Motorhome Trickle Charger

The AMT12-2 is a 2A trickle charger/battery maintainer that can maintain your campervan or motorhome battery at full charge when a solar or mains charger is used to charge a leisure battery/auxiliary battery. The trickle charger will also charge the vehicle battery if the leisure battery is above the leisure battery threshold and the vehicle battery is below the vehicle battery threshold.

The current is limited to a maximum of 3a, it also charges if the leisure battery is 0.3V (1.0V lithium) higher than the vehicle battery and the vehicles battery is less than 12.1v. This is to pool charge & optimise the retention of charge across both batteries to maintain battery life. There is no charging if the vehicle battery is flat (i.e. less than 11.5v)

The unit is shipped configured for a smart alternator vehicle, regenerative braking and acid based batteries wet/AGM/gel (setting 4 in the table in the manual) but it is easily configured by the user with the different settings for older vehicles with standard alternators or lithium batteries. There are 2 power delivery modes standard or high power for each setting, high power is used when this is a larger draw from the vehicle battery form something like a tracker or some aftermarket radios. The unit is also configured to automatically detect battery voltage and so will work with 24v batteries.

Key Features:

  • Pulsed power to maintain starter battery levels to 12.6v
  • Uses surplus power from the leisure system when excess solar or mains charging is available to maintain the starter battery
  • Configurable to modern smart alternators and older alternators
  • configurable for AGM/Wet/Gel/Lithium batteries
  • Two power settings low power and high power for when trackers are installed
  • App available advance configuration and voltage monitoring on your phone when using the Bluetooth module
  • Suitable for 12v or 24v systems

Product Name: Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Drive Away Awning
Product Description:
Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Drive Away Awning

The Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Awning is a tunnel tent style drive away awning. Complete with an attachment height of between 175-200cm, it is compatible with most campervans or van conversions with a suitable kador.

Robust and hardwearing

The durable and waterproof ripstop fabric provides a flexible and tough awning space for touring campervan holidays. The large living area space, along with generous headroom, make the Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Awning a convenient space for 2 additional guests when used with the optional inner.

Large Canopy For Extra Weather Protection

With the removable front door and the insect-proof mesh screen situated under the deep canopy area, the Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Awning allows you to sit that bit closer to nature in the large awning space.

Freestanding Flexibility

The easy drive-away design of the Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Awning provides you with the flexibility needed to head out for the day in next to no time. With the awning left on site, you can secure your pitch and store items for your return after hours of exploring with this awning. On your return, simple drive up to the awning to re-attach and be ready to use without needing to pitch up again.

Durable Dual Pole System

Using the Outwell Power Air System (pump included) alongside steel and fibreglass poles for the porch area, this drive away awning provides a great strength versus weight ratio, making it an ideal companion for your campervan adventures.

Outwell Jonesville 290SA Flex Awning Features

Movable front door with mesh and curtains.
Deep canopy.
Pre-shaped air tubes for improved headroom and space.
Easy to use valves for quick inflation/deflation.
Groundsheet with draught excluder skirt.
Hook track system.
Cable entry point.
Individually inflated rigid air beams.
Dual beading 5mm and 7mm designed to fit all campervan awning rails.
Carry bag.
Air Pump.

Specifications

Flysheet: Outtex® 6000 Express RS (RipStop), 100% polyester
Hydrostatic Head: 6000 mm
Roof connection length: 250 cm
Attachment height: 175 - 200 cm
Bead thickness: 7 mm / 5 mm
Tubes: Power Air System frame for best performance
Maximum pressure: 9 psi/0.6 bar
Poles: Steel pole 19 mm / Duratec fibreglass 8.5 mm

Colour: Green

Product Description:
Victron Kit 1 – DC-DC, 370W Solar, MultiPlus II 3000, Cerbo GX, GX Touch & Lynx

Complete Off-Grid Power & Charging System for Campervans, Motorhomes or Marine Use

This Victron Solar Panel Kit can provide 230 volt power when it's needed most. Combining the dual 185w Victron Monocrystalline panels with the impressive Victron SmartSolar MPPT 100/30 controller and MultiPlus-II 12/3000/120-32 230V Inverter/Charger, this is a powerful 230V solution for your motorhome, campervan or marine needs.

Off Grid But Not Without Power

230V AC power can be used during off grid adventures or in the event of mains power failures. The flexibility to use essential AC equipment when at remote locations can provide peace of mind and an added level of comfort. 

Smart Charging Whilst On The Move

In addition to the 370w solar panels and controller, the kit comes with the Victron Orion-Tr Smart 12 30A DC-DC charger. Smart alternator compatible, this Victron Orion-Tr Smart DC-DC charger provides a charging solution for both lead acid and lithium batteries.

Control At Your Fingertips

To help control the power behind this Victron Solar Panel Kit, it comes with the new Cerbo GX and GX Touch 50 touch screen. Monitor, control and maximise system performance via the touch screen display or smartphone compatible Bluetooth app. This control is further enhanced thanks to the Lynx Distributor for fuse status indication and Victron Battery Monitor.

Complete Kit Including Fittings

All fittings, cables, mounts, fuses and holders are included in this Victron solar panel kit.

Victron Kit 2 - 370 Watt Solar Panel with MPPT Controller, MultiPlus and Lithium Batteries
Product Description:
Victron Solar Panel Kit - A great combination of 370W Solar Panels with MPPT Controller, MultiPlus & Lithium Power

A Powerful Solar Kit For Powerful Use

Victron Kit 2 is a complete, professional-grade off-grid power system designed to deliver clean, reliable energy to campervans, caravans, motorhomes, and other mobile setups. Built around four premium Victron components, this kit provides a smart combination of solar generation, shore power charging, battery monitoring, and 230V AC power output.

Whether you’re travelling full-time, touring across the country, or staying off-grid for extended periods, this system gives you the tools to manage and monitor your energy usage with total confidence.

Victron SmartSolar MPPT 100/30 Solar Charge Controller

This high-efficiency charge controller uses maximum power point tracking (MPPT) technology to optimise solar panel performance, even in low-light conditions. It ensures your leisure battery is charged quickly and safely using solar power.

Victron Multiplus 1600/12/70 Inverter/Charger

A compact and powerful unit combining a 1600VA pure sine wave inverter and a 70A battery charger. The Multiplus allows you to power 230V appliances while off-grid and seamlessly manage shore power input when connected at a campsite or mains source. It also provides an uninterruptible AC supply by automatically switching between battery and mains.

Victron BMV-712 Smart Battery Monitor (with Shunt)

This precision battery monitor tracks real-time battery voltage, current, state of charge, and power usage. With built-in Bluetooth connectivity, you can view your system’s status via the VictronConnect app on your phone or tablet—perfect for staying in control of your energy use on the road. It also includes a shunt for accurate, system-wide measurements.

Core Components

  • Victron SmartSolar MPPT 100/30 – Solar charge controller with maximum power point tracking
  • Victron Multiplus 1600/12/70 – Combined inverter/charger for AC output and shore power charging
  • 2 x Victron 185W Monocrystalline Solar Panels – Reliable solar generation for off-grid use
  • Victron MC4 Solar Splitter Pair – Simplifies dual panel setup
  • 2 x Victron MC4 Solar Cables (5m, 6mm²) – Durable, weather-resistant cabling
  • Victron Battery Switch Isolator (275A) – For safe battery disconnection
  • Victron BMV-712 Smart Battery Monitor (Shunt)
  • Victron Wiring Packs – Pre-configured wiring for efficient installation

Protection & Distribution

  • 200A MEGA Fuse
  • 40A MIDI Fuse
  • 4-Way MIDI & Single MEGA Fuse Holder
  • 2 x 25A Mains Consumer Units
  • Negative Bus Bar (M8)

Mounting Options

Choose between Black or White mounting kits:

  • 2 x Side Mounts
  • 2 x Corner Fixings
  • 2-Way Cable Gland
  • Sikaflex 221

Battery Options

Victron Kit 2 Battery Options AGM Batteries Victron Lithium Batteries Fogstar Lithium Battery
Optional Battery Selection 2 x Victron 12V 110Ah AGM Deep Cycle Batteries 2 x Victron 12V 100Ah SuperPack Lithium Batteries 1 x Fogstar Drift 12V 230Ah Lithium Battery

Victron Kit 5 - Orion-Tr Smart DC to DC Charger Kit
Product Description:
Victron Battery to Battery Kit - Orion-Tr Smart DC-DC Charger & fittings

A Complete Alternator Charging Kit

This Victron Orion-Tr 12/12 30A DC to DC Charger Kit allows the engine of your campervan, motorhome or van conversion to charge the battery of your electrical system.

Smart Charging On The Move

Using the Victron Orion-Tr Smart 12 30A DC-DC charger, which is smart alternator compatible, it allows the battery to be topped up during journeys so it's in the best condition when you arrive at your destination. Compatible with both lead acid and lithium batteries.

Powerful Battery Backup

This kit includes a market leading Victron 100Ah Lithium battery, ideal for powering your 12v devices, lights and appliances.

Robens Arrow Head 1 Single Man Camping Tent
Product Description:
Robens Arrow Head 1 Single Man Camping Tent

One Man Lightweight Camping Tent

The Robens Arrow Head 1 is a hikers best friend, this lightweight, single-man tent constructed to be a balance of comfort and lightweight portability. Designed for quick and easy setup, this lightweight tunnel tent offers a comfortable and stable sleeping space, ideal for one camper. Its sloping tunnel design provides enhanced headroom while minimizing pack size and weight, making it perfect for backpacking trips. The Robens Arrow Head 1 is the perfect tent for mountain bikers, solo hikers, wild adventurers, trekkers, campers and cycle tourists due to its small pack size and weight, making this tent highly portable.

 

Robens Arrow Head 1 Features:

  • Side door for easy entry and exit
  • Porch area and area at feet for storage
  • Colour coded alloy poles and pole sleeves
  • Covered ventilation panels to ensure airflow during rain
  • Mesh bug panel in door
  • Lantern hanging point for easy lighting
  • Fire Retardant - The fabric does not burn. but melts when in direct contact with flames
  • 3000mm Hydrostatic Head - Resists water penetration for enhanced waterproofing
  • Taped Seams - Sealed seams ensure long-term water resistance
  • Rain Safe Vents - Hooded vents provide adjustable airflow while keeping rain out
  • Lightweight aluminium poles for strength and durability
  • Mosquito Net for bug-free ventilation
  • Packsack with roll-down closure for easy stowing

Wind Testing

Robens Wind Test: The determination of the performance of a Robens tent in wind is based on the knowledge and technique available to Robens at the time of testing. During the test we register the maximum (MAX) speed impact a tent was subjected and the average (AVG) wind speed at which structural instability occurred. This may appear as a broken/deformed pole, or the collapse of the tent and subsequent return to shape when the wind drops. At no point was any form of catastrophic failure experienced up to the maximum wind speed.
Product Warranty: The Robens Arrow Head 1 comes with a 2 year warranty

Victron Lithium SuperPack 100Ah Leisure Battery
Product Description:
Victron Energy SuperPack 100Ah Lithium Leisure Battery for Campervans, Caravans, Motorhomes & Boats

12V Off-Grid Power Battery

The Victron Energy Lithium SuperPack 12.8v LiFePO4 Leisure Battery 100Ah provides a complete, simple lithium battery solution for your off-grid motorhome or campervan. The SuperPack has an integrated BMS (Battery Management System) that offers protection from over discharge, over charge, and low or high temperatures and with an internal switch will disconnect the battery from charge if necessary. This makes the Victron Lithium SuperPack battery easy and simple to install.

Why use a Lithium-Iron-Phosphate battery over lead-acid?

Also known as LiFePO4 or LFP, Victron Lithium batteries operate well, even if the charge level is not at 100%. In fact, service life will slightly improve in case of partial instead of full charge, a significant advantage over lead-acid leisure batteries. For added safety, SuperPack batteries will cut-off the charge or discharge current when maximum ratings are met. 

Efficient Power

When comparing Li-ion to lead-acid batteries, energy efficiency is a key factor to many installations. Victron LiFePO4 Leisure Batteries can provide round-trip energy efficiency (the act of full discharge from 100% to 0% and back to full charge again) of 92% compared to 80% with lead-acid batteries. Lead-acid batteries can become significantly inefficient when the state of charge is 80% or less. This inefficiency can be particularly noticeable in solar charged systems when several days of reserve energy are required.

Weight Comparison

When comparing similar Amp-Hour rated batteries, Lithium can make substantial weight savings compared to lead-acid. Victron 12v 60Ah Deep Cycle AGM weighs 20kg whereas the equivalent 12.8v Lithium SuperPack 60Ah tips the scales at 9.5kg. 

Please Note: SuperPack batteries can be connected together in parallel but must not be connected in series.

Product Description:
Vango Tuscany Air Elements ProShield Inflatable Caravan Awning

A caravan awning featuring with top quality fabric, single point inflation system and large windows

The Vango Tuscany Air Elements ProShield Inflatable Awning features Vango's leading technology including AirBeam single point inflation and multi-point deflation system, for quick pitching or packing away. Draught Seal system for improved protection from wind accessing the awning area between the caravan and awning without additional poles.   • Optional Vango Annex Available - Providing extra storage or sleeping area

Product Name: Vango Lismore Air 450 Family Tent Package
Product Description:
Vango Lismore 450 Air Tent Package 

Spacious 4 Person Airbeam Family Tent

The Vango Lismore Air is a family tent available in a 4 person package. The 4 person model is ideally suited to couples and small families. This great value tent comes as a package which includes the tent and a footprint which helps extend the life of your tent by keeping it clean and protecting the groundsheet from stones and sharp objects.

 

The Lismore Air is a generous 3 zone tunnel tent design. The 4 man version features a comfortable bedroom with privacy divider, a spacious living area for relaxing and an additional area that can be opened up to extend the living area or opened up in front to create a covered porch area. The front awning door can be used in three positions; fully open, semi-open or closed. The side door has the option to be used as a canopy with a set of optional king poles (sold separately).  The Lismore 450 is a versatile tent with ample space on camping trips with family and friends.

 

Lights-Out inner tents and extra large bedrooms ensure a good nights sleep by keeping the tent dark when the early sun rises. Inside the bedroom are storage pockets, ideal for stowing torches and mobile phones.

 

Easy inflating AirBeam construction

Vango's AirBeam design allows for quick and easy inflation of the tent to ensure a stress free pitch every time. The fully sewn-in groundsheet keeps out draughts and bugs, whilst ventilation can be controlled with the mesh doors and AirZone panels. The Airzoine beams provide a strong and spacious living area with a convenient maximum height of over 2 metres.

 

Vango Lismore AirBeam Tent Features:

  • All flysheet seams are factory taped which provides watertight seal.
  • Dimond clear windows to maximise light and visibility with no added weight.
  • Cable entry point and lantern hanging point.
  • Fully sewn-in groundsheet adding to the comfort of your tent by providing a bug and draught free environment whilst camping.
  • Bedroom area includes pockets for conveniently storing your essentials.
  • Vango AirBeam structure with Airspeed valves for quick and easy pitching.
  • High visibility guylines making it easy to see in low light conditions.
  • Vango Nightfall bedrooms helping reduce any early morning light for an undisturbed sleep.
  • Double Action Pump.
  • Optional Universal Carpet bundle available to fit the 450 tent package.

Vango Harris 500 Poled Tent

Vango Poled 5 Person Tent with Optional Bundle Offer

The newly designed Vango Harris is a spacious tunnel tent ideal for couples and family camping. Enjoy those summer holidays in a spacious and lightweight 5 person tent. The Harris tent features three main areas; a sleeping compartment with internal divider which sleeps 5 comfortably, a spacious living area and a front covered porch area. The side entry door can be converted to another canopy with the addition of some optional king poles (sold separately).

 

The Vango Harris 500 come with multiple mesh ventilation points to keep you cool on warm camping trips. Lights-Out inner tents and extra large bedrooms ensure a good nights sleep by keeping the tent dark when the early sun rises. Inside the bedroom are storage pockets, ideal for stowing torches and mobile phones. The pre-attached front canopy provides additional space for dining or relaxing, ensuring you make the most of those longer sunny days while also providing shelter on rainy days. 

 

The Harris tent uses Sentinal fabric and light-weight fibreglass poles, reducing the pack size and weight in comparison to the air equivalent, meaning much more space in the boot of your car for camping essentials. All this while ensuring Vango's quality and durability.

 

This great value tent is available as a bundle with compatible footprint/groundsheet and universal carpet for a complete camping setup.

 

Vango Harris Poled Tent Features:

  • Vango Sentinel fabric with a lightweight yet high waterproof rating

Product Name: Victron Energy Battery Isolator Shut-Off Switch 275A
Product Description:
Victron Energy Battery Isolator Switch 275A

Safely disconnect your battery - ideal for preventing winter battery drain

This battery isolator switch can be used to isolate leisure batteries from DC loads or charge sources. When fitted, it can preserve battery charge in unattended systems e.g. in a caravan over winter. It can also be used to create a parallel connection to a secondary starter battery to jump-start in emergencies. It can be surface or panel mounted, and comes with 16 stickers to customise it for your application.

Suitable for 12v, 24v and 48v systems in campervans, caravans, motorhomes, boats and other off-grid environments.

Product Name: Alpicool Adventurer ARC22 - ARC35 20/30 Litre 12v Compressor Camping Fridge
Product Description:
Alpicool Adventurer ARC22/ARC35 - 20 and 30 Litre 12v camping and campervan coolbox fridge

Compact design fridge with efficient compressor operation

Alpicool Adventurer ARC22/ARC35 fridge provides either 22 or 35 Litres fridge storage and makes for a compact fridge solution for campervan and camping use. The 12v DC compressor is efficient and quiet, offering two running modes depending upon your needs. 

Feature full camping fridge 

The Alpicool Adventurer ARC series fridges have a three-stage battery protection system, easy to use controls with clear LED display and door latch. Generous wall insulation of the interior chamber and removable divider help to keep contents chilled and organised.

Secure mounting

Both the ARC22/ARC35 have the ability to secure the fridge base to the included mounting plate, to prevent movement during transit. This makes it ideal for campervans, van conversions, truck cabs or marine use.

Alpicool Adventurer ARC22 and ARC35 12/24v coolbox fridge:

  • Coolbox style fridge with digital temperature control panel
  • Clear LED display
  • Fully insulated body with removable divider
  • 12/24V
  • Door latch
  • Mounting plate for added security during transit

Product Description:
Alpicool Adventurer 76 Litre Wheeled 12v and Mains Portable Fridge

Rugged design with telescopic handle

The Alpicool Adventurer wheeled 76 Litre fridge freezer keeps food and drinks cold on the move. Operating from 12v DC or 230v AC, with the included adaptor, this wheeled fridge is robustly built to take on camping trips and days out.  This compressor fridge, with insulated body, also has the ability to work with an optional detachable battery to extend time away from your tent or campervan power for longer.

Built-in accessories

The Alpicool Adventurer ADW80/TSW80 portable fridge features a useful array of features, ideal for camping trips including plastic chopping board, wire storage basket, internal LED light, interior drain plug and cup holder integrated into the fridge lid. 

Digital control

 This 12 volt wheeled cool box features a digital control panel with LED display for accurate fridge temperature adjustments. This fridge has a 3 stage battery protection system and can operate on two settings for increased cooling times or extended operation.

Alpicool Adventurer 95 Litre Portable 12v and Mains Compressor Fridge

Sturdy portable cased fridge with telescopic handle

With an efficient compressor operated from 12v DC or 230v AC the Alpicool Adventurer wheeled 95 Litre fridge keeps food and drinks cold on the move. Using an optional removable battery, this wheeled fridge can chill food and drink on camping trips and days out away from your tent or campervan power for longer.

Feature rich wheeled camping fridge

The Alpicool Adventurer ADW100/TSW100 portable fridge provides lots of useful features for camping or campervan holidays. A chopping board, wire storage basket, integrated cup holder in lid, internal LED light and interior drain plug for easy cleaning. 

Digital display and control for accurate temperature adjustment 

Operating in two energy modes, ECO and MAX, and with easy touch controls and a clear LED display, using this fridge is simple and trouble free. The Alpicool Adventurer ADW100 also has a 3 stage battery protection system to prevent damaging the leisure battery of the campervan or van conversion.

Alpicool Adventurer 12v DC and 230v AC Wheeled Compressor Coolbox

Portable fridge available in a range of sizes

The Alpicool Adventurer ADENX range offers great fridge performance through an efficient compressor that can operate from 12v DC or 230v AC. With a choice of 42, 52 or 62 Litres, this range of wheeled camping fridges will keep food and drinks perfectly chilled during camping trips or campervan holidays.  

Robustly built portable cool box

With an ECO mode for energy saving operation or a fast cooling MAX option, this fridge gives you ability to choose the level of power being used. Along with the LED control panel and display, setting the fridge temperature is easy and concise.

Battery protection included

In addition to a choice of power modes, the Alpicool Adventurer ENX fridges also have a 3 stage battery protection system. This protection is designed to prevent damage of the campervan leisure battery that can occur from over discharging.

Product Description:
Alpicool Adventurer 12v Armrest Compressor Fridge

12v Armrest Fridge

This uniquely styled 15 litre fridge is designed for installation in the front cab of compatible MPV vehicles, keeping cool drinks and snacks to hand whilst travelling.   

Useful features for drivers on the move

Complete with cup holders, USB charge ports, digital display and leather fridge lid, this armrest fridge makes an ideal accessory for drivers. 

Removable optional battery available

The Adventurer 12v armrest fridge is available with a removable battery for use when the vehicle engine is not running. This can prevent food and drinks becoming warm during periods in between journeys. It also has a 3 stage battery protection system. This protection is designed to prevent damage of the vehicle battery that can occur from over discharging.

Product Name: Alpicool Adventurer 12v & Mains Dual Compartment Rugged Camping Compressor Fridge
Product Description:
Alpicool Dual Compartment 12v DC - 230v AC Camping Fridge

Independently controllable camping fridge freezer

Available in either a 35, 45 or 55 litre versions, these Alpicool Adventurer camping fridges provide the flexibility to operate dual compartments as either a fridge or freezer for complete control over storing chilled or frozen food and drinks. This allows you to store fresh meat, seafood or ice cream at the desired temperature. These cool boxes are highly portable, with its durable wheels and telescopic handle, and a durable design which makes these coolboxes ideal for camping and caravanning holidays.

Sturdy robust design

The Alpicool TAW range of fridges are designed for the rough and tough of camp life. From heavy duty handles and anti-vibration construction to internal LED lights and low noise operation, The Alpicool TAW models make for ideal fridges for camping or van conversion holidays.

Easy operation controls and display

With a clear LED display and touch controls, this fridge can be easily set to the running temperature of you choosing with the efficient compressor motor. It also has a 3 stage battery protection system, to prevent damage of the leisure battery that can occur from over discharging during operation. A optional removable battery and solar panel is available to provide useful chilling function when away from 12v DC power. Ideal for extended days on the beach or countryside.

Alpicool Adventurer TAW35-TAW45-TAW55 dual compartment camping fridge:

  • Efficient Cooling
  • Choice of 35L, 45L or 55L capacity
  • Built-in Car Battery Protection
  • Highly Portable
  • Dual Temperature Control
  • Built-in LED Light Design
  • Drain Plug
  • Two Detachable Door Lids
  • Cutting Board
  • Two Cup Slots
  • Bottle Opener
  • Optional removable battery available
